Sɣur Murad Muḥand Saɛid ([[Wp/kab/Tidukkla Tadelsant Tamaziɣt di Uṭṭawa-Ḥull|'''Tidukkla Tadelsant Tamaziɣt di Uṭṭawa-Ḥull''']]) 


As n sebt-nni yezrin ( 24 di fuṛaṛ 2007) i tikelt nniḍen
tuɣal-d tcequft umezgun Tidak n Nna Fa, ar Munṛiyal. Nna Fa akken
i daɣ-tṛegem, teseḍs-aɣ, tesru-yaɣ
ciṭuḥ, tesmekta-yaɣ-d ayen akken nɣil nettu-t, netta
ziɣ izdeɣ-aɣ deg ul. Segw akken, Nna Fa tuska-d af wul n
yemnezhen, tuɣal d tajidatt akw n widak i tt-iwalan.
Af akken i d-qublen imnezhen tacequft Tidak n Nna Fa, ur d-yegwri ccek,
leqbayel ḥemlen amezgun. Sekra n win inezhen, yesteqsa-d : melmi ara d
yeffeɣ uḍebsi (DVD) n tcequft ? melmi ara das-d-aɛwdem? Ad
testthegim tacequft tamaynutt ?
Udem-nni swayes imnezhen qublen-d tacequft, yefka i widak i d-yuraren afud
ameqwṛan. Alami aṭas i yɣilen d ṭbib n tidett, d
tamɣaṛt n tidett i yellan zdat-sen!. Lfeṛḥ n
yemnezhen, yefka aɛwin usegwas i widak i d-ihegan tacequft n Tidak n
Nna Fa.
Mačči kan ala tacequft s timad-is i ysefṛaḥen, ula d
leqdic, d uhegi, dayen yesfeṛḥen widak i d-yusan: tacequft tebda
di lweqt, yal taɣawsa di lweqt-is. Nnan widak i nezhen: tasekurt
timelalin.


